{
  "page": "Did you know/88",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that, when the <a href=\"/index.php/Lorathi\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lorathi\">Lorathi</a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Qarlon_the_Great\" title=\"Qarlon the Great\">Qarlon the Great</a> laid siege on <a href=\"/index.php/Norvos\" title=\"Norvos\">Norvos</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a> rose to defend her daughter, resulting in the <a href=\"/index.php/Scouring_of_Lorath\" title=\"Scouring of Lorath\">Scouring of Lorath</a>? No man, woman, or child survived, and Lorath was uninhabited for more than a century thereafter.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/88&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities: Lorath.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404003854\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 secon